<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/446484-i-found-the-writing-to-be-very-didactic">I found the writing to be very didactic and showing off a bit. The sentences do go on. I haven&#39;t read very much yet and will struggle on but it is not bedtime reading. Did you find the language too wordy ?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_446484'><a id="like_count_community_question_446484" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/446484?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">35 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F2967752-the-elegance-of-the-hedgehog">like</a></span>

