<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/15888444-garden-gal">Garden Gal</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is not a small, easy book. IT IS a book for teens and adults who do not mind thinking as they read.<br/>It is difficult to read at a single sitting be<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is not a small, easy book. IT IS a book for teens and adults who do not mind thinking as they read.<br />It is difficult to read at a single sitting because it will stimulate thought, and perhaps journaling.<br /><br />I have read it only twice to date,and made discoveries on the second reading. Share it and talk about it with other readers.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
